| **Bootstrap/DI** | `/Users/135yshr/go/src/github.com/SecureCycle/ai-monitoring-backend-go/internal/app/bootstrap/` |
| **Shared DI** | `/Users/135yshr/go/src/github.com/SecureCycle/ai-monitoring-backend-go/internal/shared/di/container.go` |
| **Error Handling** | `/Users/135yshr/go/src/github.com/SecureCycle/ai-monitoring-backend-go/pkg/apperror/codes.go` |
| **Users Module** | `/Users/135yshr/go/src/github.com/SecureCycle/ai-monitoring-backend-go/internal/users/` |
